name: The Deck
title: The Deck – A Hub for Card Games that Bring People Together
description: The Deck is a simple hub for card-based apps like Common Ground, Family Cards, Couple Cards, Survival Cards, and more — all designed to spark connection, unity, and fun.
author: Michael Schwartz
